## Hello 👋
This repo contain useful bash script to make life easy as a linux poweruser 
you can use it as want !

### Step to Use 
**Step 1:** `Download script from my repo`
**Step 2:** give permission to that script file
```bash
chmod 764 cloud
```
you can replace `cloud` with `script` you will use  

**Step 3:** to execute just 
go to that directory then
```bash
./cloud
```
again replace `cloud` with `script` you will use 

